Name: Identity Routing Document (IRD)
Description: a top-level routing table for a DID's resources

Name: Profiles Routing Document (PRD)
Description: a routing table for a DID's profiles

Name: Keychain Routing Document (KRD)
Description: a routing table for a DID's authentication keychains

Name: Accounts Routing Document (ARD)
Description: a routing table for a DID's external accounts

Name: Connections Routing Document (CRD)
Description: a routing table for a DID's social connections

Name: Sources Routing Document (SORD)
Description: a routing table for a DID's external data sources

Name: Services Routing Document (SERD)
Description: a routing table for a DID's services
